T16TD4437E:294a-6: spos dkar rnams kyi bdug pa byas na myur du tshong 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4437E:294a-7: sgog pa zos na aa ru dang /
T16TD4437E:294a-8: ku ta btags na dri ma med par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4437E:294a-9: chang btungs nas durba btags na dri ma med par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4437E:294a-10: pa ro l'i'i khu ba btab na chang dkar por 'gyur ro //
T16TD4437E:294a-12: so so b'i ra btab na rang bzhin du gnas par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4437E:294a-13: k'a ra sum kha dkar po'i rtsa ba dang rma bya'i gzug phud kyi rtsa ba dang /
T16TD4437E:294a-14: gzhan gyis mi thub pa dkar po'i rtsa ba rnams gcig tu byas nas btags te grib ma la bskams pa'i ril bu khar bcug cing /
T16TD4437E:294a-15: lus la byug pa byas na g-yul las mtshon cha bzlog par byed do //
T16TD4437E:294a-16: skyu ru ra'i rtsa ba dang /
T16TD4437E:294a-17: me tog phyung nas khar bcug na g-yul las mtshon cha rengs par byed do //
T16TD4437E:294a-18: au ddhaddhag li tam ba n'a ni sikta mritti k'am gri hya dakto da ra ma dhye prak'i sya ya ta gri ha phat la sth'a yeta /
T16TD4437E:294a-19: ta tra aishmi k'a ya tanti /
T16TD4437E:294a-21: ba hu b'a ra briksha sya dakshi na s'a kh'am gri hya ka ra yi tv'a shrirga ma t'ishma sha dagni /
T16TD4437E:294a-24: lha ma bu chu gsher gyi chu dang /
T16TD4437E:294a-29: ga na ka'i sa bon dang /
T16TD4437E:294a-30: 'di dag gis bdugs pa'i ril bu sbyar te /
T16TD4437E:294a-31: bdug spos 'dis rnyed pa dang bcas pa'i tshong 'gyur [?] bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4437E:294a-33: aom na mo tsanda ku sha ku ru ku ru sv'a h'a//
T16TD4437E:294a-34: 'di ni byams pa gling gi gzims khang du rgya dpe bzhugs pa las chos rje rin po che ngag gi dbang phyug bsod nams rnam rgyal dpal bzang po'i bka' bzhin du /
T16TD4437E:294a-35: zha lu lo ts'a ba dge slong chos skyong bzang pos rgya dpe bzhin ji ltar go ba rnams bsgyur ba'o /
T16TD4437E:294b-0: // / bla ma @294b dang sangs rgyas sman gyi bla drang srong tshe'i rig byed 'dzin pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4437E:294b-1: thog mar nad kyi mtshan nyid brtag pa ni //
T16TD4437E:294b-2: pho ba'i nad rnams rlung la brten /
T16TD4437E:294b-3: sems 'khrul pa dang za zir 'byung ba mkhris pa la brten /
T16TD4437E:294b-4: rang bzhin gyis 'khrul pa bad kan la brten /
T16TD4437E:294b-5: tshad pa ma 'ju ba la brten /
T16TD4437E:294b-6: rlung gi tshad pa'i nad yun gyi tshad zhag bdun /
T16TD4437E:294b-8: bad kan tshad ba zhag bcu gnyis /
T16TD4437E:294b-9: rlung tshad kyi brtag pa ni /
T16TD4437E:294b-10: tshigs rnams brdungs pa lta bur na /
T16TD4437E:294b-11: g-yal stong 'byung zhing bya snyong byed snying 'dod /
T16TD4437E:294b-14: mgo dang chu rgyus rtsib logs mur gong rkang mthil rnams lhag par na /
T16TD4437E:294b-18: mig dang sen mo shin tu dmar /
T16TD4437E:294b-20: de rnams tshang ba 'am shas chen nges par rlung dang ldan pa'o //
T16TD4437E:294b-21: rtags de rnams shas che zhing rtsar mkhris pa dang bad kan gnyis ka 'dug na 'dus pa'i rtags so //
T16TD4437E:294b-23: chu yang yang 'tshag snying 'dod cing btsags tshe na zug kyang cung zad 'byung /
T16TD4437E:294b-26: kha'i nang dang lce sogs la thor pa chung ngu mang du 'byung /
T16TD4437E:294b-28: mig mnan pa lta bu 'degs dka'/
T16TD4437E:294b-30: mig dang sen mo mdog ser /
T16TD4437E:294b-33: de rnams tshang ba 'am shas che na mkhris pa ldan pa'o //
T16TD4437E:294b-34: rtags 'di rnams shas che zhing rtsar rlung rtsa dang bad kan gnyis ka 'dug na 'dus ba'i nad kyi rtags so //
T16TD4437E:294b-36: lus dang shes pa lci bas gang yang byed mi 'dod pa /
T16TD4437E:294b-37: dang kha 'gags shing zas gang la'ang bro ba med /
T16TD4437E:294b-38: mig mnan pa lta bur lci ba /
T16TD4437E:294b-40: lus la drod cung zad yod pa /
T16TD4437E:294b-43: mchil ma mang du 'byung zhing skyur dgos pa /
T16TD4437E:294b-44: lus mdog mdangs med thal kha dang tshi che /
T16TD4437E:295a-2: de rnams tshang ba'am shas che na bad kan yin zhing /
T16TD4437E:295a-3: gong gi rtags rnams phal cher tshang la rtsar rlung dang mkhris pa gnyis ka ldan pa 'dus pa'i rtags so //
T16TD4437E:295a-4: gzhan yang 'dus pa'i rtags la gtam chal chol smra /
T16TD4437E:295a-6: mig dmar zhing mchi ma 'dzag / lce 'gags so //
T16TD4437E:295a-7: nad glo bur ba'i rtags la /
T16TD4437E:295a-8: mig mdongs nas blta nan che zhing g-yo 'gul nyung /
T16TD4437E:295a-10: de ltar rtags dang rtsa mthun na rkyang pa dang /
T16TD4437E:295a-11: dper na rlung gi rtags la mkhris pa'i rtsa /
T16TD4437E:295a-12: mkhris pa'i rtags la rlung gi rtsa lta bu 'dug na mkhris rlung ste des rigs bsgres te shes par bya'o //
T16TD4437E:295a-14: rtsa ba rlung mkhris bad kan gsum gyi rtsa /
T16TD4437E:295a-15: de las gyes pa bcu bzhi ste /
T16TD4437E:295a-18: bad kan dang nye ba'i rlung /
T16TD4437E:295a-19: mkhris pa'i gnas su mkhris pa /
T16TD4437E:295a-22: bad kan dang nye ba'i mkhris pa /
T16TD4437E:295a-23: bad kan gyi gnas su bad kan /
T16TD4437E:295a-26: mkhris pa dang nye ba'i bad kan te bcu gnyis /
T16TD4437E:295a-27: gsum ga'i gnas su rgyu ba'i khrag dang chu'i rtsa ste bcu bzhi'o //
T16TD4437E:295a-28: de la rlung gi rtsa ni sbom la mgyogs /
T16TD4437E:295a-29: mkhris pa'i rtsa ni grims la mgyogs /
T16TD4437E:295a-30: bad kan gyi rtsa ni lhod la da la ba yin la /
T16TD4437E:295a-31: de yang zhogs pa lus ma 'khrugs shing zas gang yang ma zos gong du blta ste mkhrig ma'i gnyer ma dang po nas rim bzhin nam mkha'/
T16TD4437E:295a-35: sa lnga las nam mkha' dang sa'i gnas por ba'i rlung me chu gsum gyi gnas mtshon kan chag gsum gyi 'og tu rim pa ltar rlung mkhris bad kan gsum gyi gnas su bzung la /
T16TD4437E:295a-38: bad kan gyi gnas gyi rlung gsum /
T16TD4437E:295a-39: de yang rlung gnas rang gi rlung rtsa sarba sbrul gyi 'gros lta bur 'phar /
T16TD4437E:295a-40: mkhris gnas kyi rlung (bha ai pa) bya rog gi 'gros ltar 'phar /
T16TD4437E:295a-41: bad kan gnas kyi rlung rma (may'u ra) bya'i 'gros ltar 'phar /
T16TD4437E:295b-0: de bzhin du mkhris gnas rang gi mkhris rtsa (la ba)...sreg @295b pa 'phur ba ltar 'phar /
T16TD4437E:295b-1: rlung gnas kyi mkhris rtsa shig gi 'gros ltar 'phar /
T16TD4437E:295b-2: bad kan gnas kyi mkhris rtsa 'bab chu ltar 'phar ba /
T16TD4437E:295b-3: bad kan rang gnas kyi rtsa ngang pa'i rgyal po'i 'gros ltar 'phar /
T16TD4437E:295b-4: rlung gnas kyi bad kan gyi rtsa srin 'bu padma can gyi 'gros ltar 'phar /
T16TD4437E:295b-5: mkhris gnas kyi bad kan gyi rtsa sbal ba'i 'gros (dzum) ltar 'phar /
T16TD4437E:295b-6: khrag la'ang gsum ste rlung (p'a ni) gnas kyi khrag rtsa nya'i 'gros ltar 'phar /
T16TD4437E:295b-7: (ham sa r'a dza) mkhris gnas kyi khrag rtsa bye'u'i skad ltar 'phar /
T16TD4437E:295b-8: (dzo lu ka) bad kan gnas kyi khrag rtsa phu ron gyi 'gros ltar 'phar /
T16TD4437E:295b-9: chu la (mandu ka) gnyis te rlung gnas dang mkhris gnas kyi chu'i rtsa rta'i 'gros ltar 'phar /
T16TD4437E:295b-10: bad kan (ma tsha li) gnas kyi gnas kyi chu'i rtsa khyim bya'i 'gros ltar 'phar la /
T16TD4437E:295b-11: rlung (ci ri) gi gnas su sbrul gyi 'gros ltar 'phar na rang gnas su rang (ka b'u tra/) /'gros te nad med kyi rtsa /
T16TD4437E:295b-12: sreg pa'i 'gros ltar 'phar na mkhris rlung gi nad tshan (re wa) che zhing bcos dka'/
T16TD4437E:295b-14: (kukshu ti) shig gi 'gros ltar 'phar na mkhris rlung yin kyang tshan chung la bcos sla /
T16TD4437E:295b-15: go rim de bzhin ngang ba'i rgyal po sbal pa srin bu padma can gyi 'gros ltar 'phar na pad rlung che 'bring chung gsum /
T16TD4437E:295b-16: nya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na khrag rlung yin kyang tshan chung /
T16TD4437E:295b-17: bye'u ltar 'phar na khrag rlung 'bring po /
T16TD4437E:295b-18: phug ron ltar 'phar na khrag rlung gi nad babs lci /
T16TD4437E:295b-19: de bzhin du rta'i 'gros ltar 'phar na rlung gi chu gso sla /
T16TD4437E:295b-20: khyim bya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na gzhi che /
T16TD4437E:295b-21: mkhris pa'i gnas su sreg pa 'phur ba ltar 'phar na rang gnas su rang ste nad med kyi rtsa /
T16TD4437E:295b-22: sbrul dang rma bya'i 'gros bya rog gi skad gsum rim pa ltar mkhris rlung che 'bring chung gsum /
T16TD4437E:295b-23: ngang pa'i rgyal po srin 'bu padma can /
T16TD4437E:295b-24: sbal pa gsum gyi 'gros ltar 'phar na bad mkhris che 'bring chung gsum /
T16TD4437E:295b-25: byi'u'i skad ltar 'phar na khrag mkhris chung ngu /
T16TD4437E:295b-26: nya dang khyim bya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na khrag mkhris tshan che /
T16TD4437E:296a-2: khyim bya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na gzhi che /
T16TD4437E:296a-3: bad kan gyi gnas su ngang pa'i rgyal po'i 'gros ltar 'phar na rang gnas su rang ste nad med /
T16TD4437E:296a-4: sbrul dang bya rog rma bya gsum rim pa ltar bad rlung che 'bring chung gsum /
T16TD4437E:296a-5: sreg pa shig chu gsum bad mkhris che 'bring chung gsum /
T16TD4437E:296a-6: nya byi'u phug ron gsum bad khrag che 'bring chung gsum /
T16TD4437E:296a-7: rta'i 'gros ltar 'phar na chu dang bad kan shas che /
T16TD4437E:296a-8: khyim bya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na chu dang bad kan yin kyang shas chung ngo /
T16TD4437E:296a-9: de yang mtshon gyi mas sner mkhris rtsa dang /
T16TD4437E:296a-10: dkan gyi yas sner rlung rtsa /
T16TD4437E:296a-11: dkan gyi mas sner bad kan gyi rtsa dang /
T16TD4437E:296a-12: chag gi yas sner mkhris pa'i rtsa 'phar na nye ba'i gnas yin pas skyon chung ngo //
T16TD4437E:296a-13: rlung gi gnas su mkhris rtsa shig gi 'gros ltar 'phar na rlung mkhris yin kyang bcos na myur du bde zhing ma bcos kyang 'tsho'o //
T16TD4437E:296a-14: rlung gnas su bad kan gyi rtsa srin bu padma can gyi 'gres ltar 'phar na mgo na /
T16TD4437E:296a-15: glo dgog pa sogs 'byung zhing skyon chung yang ma bcos na ngang pa'i rgyal po'i 'gros ltar song dogs pa'i nyen yod do //
T16TD4437E:296a-16: 'bral du nad zug gzer che yang rlung gi gnas su khrag gi rtsanya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na bcos kyang myur du bde zhing ma bcos kyang mi ring bar 'tsho ba'o //
T16TD4437E:296a-17: rlung gi gnas su chu'i rtsa rta'i 'gros lta bu 'phar na dbugs kha mi bde ba /
T16TD4437E:296a-18: mig dmar zhing mig 'dag mang ba sogs 'byung /
T16TD4437E:296a-19: mkhris pa'i gnas su rlung rtsa bya rog gi 'gros ltar 'phar na kha skam skom dad che /
T16TD4437E:296a-20: tshags tshigs sogs khol bur na yang gso sla /
T16TD4437E:296a-21: mkhris pa'i gnas su bad kan gyi rtsa sbal pa'i 'gros ltar 'phar na mgo bo na /
T16TD4437E:296a-22: kha nas mchi la ma yang yang 'bo dgos shing mkhris pa'ang cung zad skyug go / mkhris pa'i gnas su khrag gi rtsa byi'u'i skad ltar 'phar na lus la rtse yas byed ci nas khrag cung zad 'dzag pa dang /
T16TD4437E:296b-0: mig gi @296b mdangs dmar ser du 'ong ngo //
T16TD4437E:296b-1: mkhris pa'i gnas su chu'i rtsa rta'i 'gros lta bur 'phar na dangs ma 'dzag / lus 'khyoms shing 'khor /
T16TD4437E:296b-2: mig na zhing mig chu 'dzag go / bad kan gyi gnas su rlung gi rtsa rma bya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na lus grang shum byed cing rkang lag gi mgo drod med /
T16TD4437E:296b-4: zhag chung zhing skya thalapho ba sbos pa dang 'khrog pa 'byung ngo //
T16TD4437E:296b-5: bad kan gyi gnas su mkhris pa'i rtsa 'bab chu'i 'gros ltar 'phar na glo dgog / brang tsha /
T16TD4437E:296b-7: bad kan gyi gnas su khrag gi rtsa phug ron gyi 'gros ltar 'phar na lus drod che /
T16TD4437E:296b-9: 'og sgor khrag cung zad 'dzag /'phongs lug pa sogs 'byung /
T16TD4437E:296b-10: bad kan gyi gnas su rtsa khyim bya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na tshigs na zhing cung zad skrangs pa /
T16TD4437E:296b-11: lus kyi mdangs mi gsal zhing tshi che ;
T16TD4437E:296b-13: rlung gi gnas su mkhris pa'i rtsa sreg pa 'phur ba lta bur 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:296b-16: lus las rdul mang du 'dzag / lus gyong /
T16TD4437E:296b-18: chu ser por 'bab pa sogs 'byung zhing 'di ni mkhris rlung gi gtso bo ste bcos la bzab bo //
T16TD4437E:296b-19: rlung gi sa ru mkhris pa'i rlung gi rtsa bya rog gi 'gros lta bur 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:296b-23: lus la thor pa dang shu ba sogs 'byung ngo //
T16TD4437E:296b-24: rlung gi gnas su mkhris pa'i bad kan gyi rtsa sbal pa'i 'gros ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:296b-31: rlung gi gnas su mkhris pa'i khrag gi rtsa byi'u'i 'gros ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:296b-33: tshags tshigs dang mgo bo na /
T16TD4437E:296b-35: rlung gi gnas su mkhris pa'i chu'i rtsa rta'i 'gros ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:296b-36: so rnyil skrangs shing chu ser dang khrag 'byung /
T16TD4437E:297a-4: rlung gi gnas su bad kan gyi rtsa ngang pa'i rgyal po'i 'gros ltar 'phar na lus brdungs shing gcus pa ltar na /
T16TD4437E:297a-8: chu gtong dka' ba sogs 'byung zhing 'di ni bad rlung gi gtso bo ste bcos la bzab bo //
T16TD4437E:297a-9: rlung gi gnas su bad kan gyi rlung gi rtsa rma bya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na pho ba gcus pa ltar na /
T16TD4437E:297a-11: rked pa dang chu rgyus na /
T16TD4437E:297a-13: rlung gi gnas su bad kan gyi mkhris pa'i rtsa 'bab chu'i 'gros ltar 'phar na brang tsha /
T16TD4437E:297a-16: mig dang sen mo'i mdog ljang khur snang ba /
T16TD4437E:297a-18: rlung gi gnas su bad kan gyi khrag gi rtsa phug ron gyi 'gros ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:297a-19: rdul 'dzag / shu ba dang thor pa 'ong //
T16TD4437E:297a-20: mig dmar zhing 'byed 'dzums nyung ba sogs 'byung ngo //
T16TD4437E:297a-21: rlung gi gnas su bad kan gyi chu'i rtsa khyim bya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na mig 'grib /
T16TD4437E:297a-25: za 'phrug long zhing brad pa dang chu ser 'dzag / pho bar srin 'bu 'phel ba sogs 'byung ngo //
T16TD4437E:297a-26: mkhris gnas su rlung gi rtsa sbrul lta bur 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:297a-27: lus kyi tshags tshigs brdungs pa ltar na /
T16TD4437E:297a-29: kha skom zhing thor pa mang /
T16TD4437E:297a-32: pho ba na ba sogs 'byung zhing 'di ni mkhris rlung gtso bo ste bcos la bzab pa gces /
T16TD4437E:297a-33: mkhris gnas su rlung gi mkhris pa'i rtsa shig gi 'gros ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:297a-37: kha rlungs dang rkang mthil drod che ba sogs 'byung /
T16TD4437E:297a-38: mkhris gnas su rlung gi bad kan gyi rtsa srin bu pad ma can ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:297b-0: khar ro kha ba @297b sogs 'byung ngo //
T16TD4437E:297b-1: mkhris gnas su rlung gi khrag rtsa nya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:297b-2: lus mdog dmar zhing ba spu'i bu ga nas khrag kyang cung zad 'jag / mig chu mang ba sogs 'byung ngo //
T16TD4437E:297b-3: mkhris gnas su rlung gi rtsa rta'i 'gros ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:297b-5: yan lag skam zhing tshigs dang gdong skrangs /
T16TD4437E:297b-6: dri chu khrag ltar bab pa sogs 'byung /
T16TD4437E:297b-7: mkhris gnas su bad kan gyi rtsa ngang pa'i rgyal po'i 'gros ltar 'phar na khar ro mngar /
T16TD4437E:297b-9: khog par zo ba'i zho drag chags pa lta bu 'byung ngo //
T16TD4437E:297b-10: lus kyi gting drod cung zad che zhing tshags tshigs sogs khol bur na /
T16TD4437E:297b-11: mkhris skran 'cha' ba sogs 'byung ste bad mkhris kyi gtso bo yin pas bcos la gzab pa gces so //
T16TD4437E:297b-12: mkhris pa'i gnas su bad kan gyi rlung gi rtsa rma bya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na /

T16TD4437E:297b-17: mkhris pa'i gnas su bad kan gyi mkhris rtsa chu'i 'gros lta bur 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:297b-21: khrag cung zad skyug pa sogs 'byung ngo //
T16TD4437E:297b-22: mkhris pa'i gnas su bad kan gyi khrag rtsa phug ron gyi 'gros ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:297b-27: mkhris pa'i gnas su bad kan gyi chu'i rtsa khyim bya'i 'gros lta bur 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:297b-30: ma 'ju ba'i nad dang 'gro 'dug dka' ba sogs 'byung /

T16TD4437E:297b-36: chu'i mdog ser ba sogs 'byung ste 'di ni bad rlung gi rtsa ba yin pas gzab bar bcos /
T16TD4437E:297b-37: bad kan gyi gnas sa rlung gi mkhris rtsa shig gi 'gros ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:298a-3: bad kan gyi gnas su rlung gi bad kan gyi rtsa srin bu pad ma can gyi 'gros ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:298a-4: be snabs skyug cing glo che /
T16TD4437E:298a-5: skya rbab dang mig 'dag mang ba sogs 'byung ngo /
T16TD4437E:298a-6: bad kan gyi gnas su rlung gi khrag gi rtsa nya'i 'gros ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:298a-8: dangs ma skams pas lus stobs nyams /
T16TD4437E:298a-10: nyin re mos kyis na ba'o //

T16TD4437E:298a-12: pags nad khol bu na ba sen mo btab kyang reg pa mi tshor ba /
T16TD4437E:298a-14: dangs ma 'dzag / lus mgo mjug thams cad na ba sogs 'byung /
T16TD4437E:298a-15: bad kan gyi gnas su mkhris pa'i rtsa sreg pa 'phur ba ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:298a-18: zas skom mi 'dod pa dang chu skyur skyug / lus drod che ba sogs 'byung ste /
T16TD4437E:298a-19: 'di yang bad mkhris gyi gtso bo yin pas bcos la bzab /
T16TD4437E:298a-20: bad kan gyi gnas su mkhris pa'i rlung rtsa bya rog gi 'gros ltar 'phar na /
T16TD4437E:298a-22: mas rlung gyen du ldog / gzhang 'brum 'ong ba sogs 'byung /
T16TD4437E:298a-23: bad kan gyi gnas su mkhris pa'i bad kan gyi rtsa sbal pa'i 'gros ltar 'phar na /

T16TD4437E:298a-27: bad kan gyi gnas su mkhris pa'i khrag gi rtsa byi'u'i skad ltar 'phar na /
